  npcName: William
  dialogueLines:
  - Hi Player, nice going! this is our little ghost town
  - you wont be able to purchase anything here, we don't get many human visters and
    we have no need for belongings
  - however if you walk around you may stumble on some chests
  - feel free to take whats in them, like I said us spirts have no need for belongings
  - ...
  - well go in! we don't bite, only zombies do that
  - zombies? well the fracture brought them, they roam around so be cautious
